RECOMMENDATION: Limit consumption to no more than 2 drinks (e.g., 24 oz beer, 10 oz wine, or 3 oz 80-proof whiskey) per day in most men, and to no more than 1 drink per day in women and lighter weight person.

August 2004
Moderation of alcohol consumption
Class.rdfs:comment:
Men: limit to <= 2 drinks per day. Women and lighter weight persons: limit to <= 1 drink per day.
